OL,3,CBorders campaign group make fresh
OL,4,Ccalls for railway extension
OL,6,FCampaigners are making fresh calls to
OL,7,Fextend the Borders Railway after plans
OL,8,Ffor a new #400m holiday park near
OL,9,FHawick were revealed.
OL,11,FCenter Parcs wants to build its first
OL,12,FScottish holiday village which aims to
OL,13,Fcreate more than 1,200 jobs.
OL,15,FMarion Short, Campaigner for Borders
OL,16,FRail, believes people from Hawick see
OL,17,Fa "correlation between the railway and
OL,18,Fthis new development."
