OL,6,FShe said: "From the campaign's
OL,7,Fperspective we see closely aligned
OL,8,Fobjectives between both of us because
OL,9,Fthey talk about economic growth.
OL,11,F"We want the railway to encourage
OL,12,Feconomic growth so therefore we should
OL,13,Fboth work together to achieve this,
OL,14,Fnot just for Hawick but for southern
OL,15,FScotland.
