OL,6,F"It's not just about bringing the
OL,7,Ftourists. If they're talking about
OL,8,Femploying hundreds of people then we
OL,9,Fneed the people who are working there
OL,10,Fto have an easier way of reaching
OL,11,Ftheir employment... it's also the
OL,12,Fcontractors at the very beginning and
OL,13,Fthey're talking about employing 800
OL,14,Fpeople thereafter."
OL,16,FThe Borders Railway Group are calling
OL,17,Ffor the train line to be extended
OL,18,Fbetween Tweedbank and Carlisle.
