OL,6,FStuart Marshall, an independent
OL,7,FCouncillor for Hawick and Denholm,
OL,8,Fsays the proposals will be a boost for
OL,9,Fthe local area.
OL,11,FHe said: "Like every other town
OL,12,Fthroughout the country we have a high
OL,13,Fstreet that has suffered badly. We
OL,14,Fhave public conveniences that need to
OL,15,Fbe looked at, electric charging
OL,16,Fpoints, better road and railway
OL,17,Fconnectivity and bus links.
