OL,6,F"Everything now needs to be in the
OL,7,Fmix, like my colleagues we are just so
OL,8,Fhappy and we'll roll up our sleeves
OL,9,Fand try and address those issues."
OL,11,FThe company will submit a planning
OL,12,Fapplication for 700 holiday lodges -
OL,13,Flocated three miles north of Hawick -
OL,14,Fin 2025.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, Colin McKinlay,
OL,17,FChief Executive Officer of Center
OL,18,FParcs, said the plans will "transform
OL,19,Fleisure and tourism" in the Scottish
OL,20,FBorders.
