OL,4,Ccalls for railway extension
OL,6,FHe added: "Many Scottish families
OL,7,Falready visit Center Parcs villages in
OL,8,FEngland, and this village will offer
OL,9,Fthe chance for people to enjoy their
OL,10,Fholidays closer to home, which in turn
OL,11,Fwill benefit the local economy."
OL,13,FThis year both the UK and Scottish
OL,14,FGovernment promised #5m towards a
OL,15,Ffeasibility study for a potential
OL,16,Frailway extension.
